Package com.github.siroshun09.mccommand.common.argument.parser

Interface ArgumentParser<T>

Type Parameters:
T - the value type
All Known Implementing Classes:
MaterialParser, PlayerExactParser, PlayerParser, ProxiedPlayerParser, SoundParser, UUIDParser
Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface
public interface ArgumentParser<T>
Parses an argument from a String
